678 void SP2::Update(double dt)
679 {
680  float LSPEED = 10.f;
681  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('1')) //enable back face culling
682  glEnable(GL_CULL_FACE);
683  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('2')) //disable back face culling
684  glDisable(GL_CULL_FACE);
685  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('3'))
686  glPolygonMode(GL_FRONT_AND_BACK, GL_FILL); //default fill mode
687  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('4'))
688  glPolygonMode(GL_FRONT_AND_BACK, GL_LINE); //wireframe mode
689  if(MenuKey == true)
690  {
691  INSTRUCTIONS1 = "Press 8 for Thief";
692  INSTRUCTIONS2 = "Press 9 for Stocker";
693  INSTRUCTIONS3 = "Press 0 for Guard";
694  INSTRUCTIONS4 = "Press Esc to quit";
695  }
696  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('8'))
697  {
698  ROLE = "Thief";
699  INSTRUCTIONS1 = "";
700  INSTRUCTIONS2 = "";
701  INSTRUCTIONS3 = "";
702  INSTRUCTIONS4 = "";
703  MenuKey = false;
704  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('9')||Application::IsKeyPressed('0'))
705  ROLE = "Thief";
706  }
707  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('9'))
708  {
709  ROLE = "Stocker";
710  INSTRUCTIONS1 = "";
711  INSTRUCTIONS2 = "";
712  INSTRUCTIONS3 = "";
713  INSTRUCTIONS4 = "";
714  MenuKey = false;
715  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('8')||Application::IsKeyPressed('0'))
716  ROLE = "Stocker";
717  }
718  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('0'))
719  {
720  ROLE = "Guard";
721  INSTRUCTIONS1 = "";
722  INSTRUCTIONS2 = "";
723  INSTRUCTIONS3 = "";
724  INSTRUCTIONS4 = "";
725  MenuKey = false;
726  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('9')||Application::IsKeyPressed('8'))
727  ROLE = "Guard";
728  }
729  if ( ItemName == "Camera")
730  {
731  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('5'))
732  {
733  camera.setCameraState(1);
734  camera.CameraMode = true;
735  }
736 
737  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('6'))
738  {
739  camera.setCameraState(2);
740  camera.CameraMode = true;
741  }
742  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('7'))
743  {
744  camera.setCameraState(0);
745  camera.CameraMode = false;
746  }
747  }
748 
749  CheckItem();
750  DoorSlide();
751  ShutterOpen();
752  NPCwalk();
753  NPCShop();
754  if (camera.getCameraState() == 0)
755  {
756  CharacterCrouch();
757  UIupdates(dt);
758  BoundsCheck();
759  SetPrevPos();
760  UnpaidItems();
761  camera.Update(dt);
762  Stealing();
763  }
764  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 1)
765  {
766  Security1.Update(dt);
767  }
768  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 2)
769  {
770  Security2.Update(dt);
771  }
772 
773  if ( police == true)
774  {
775  if ( EscapeEnd == true)
776  {
777  EscapeCarMove++;
778  }
779 
780  for ( int i =0; i<PoliceMan.ReadTextFilePoliceSize(); ++i)
781  {
782  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->getItemPrice() <= 0 )
783  {
784  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->setItemAvailable(false);
785  }
786  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->getItemAvailability() == false)
787  {
788  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD < 20)
789  {
790  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD += (1*dt);
791  }
792  else if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD > 20)
793  {
794  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->resethealth();
795  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD = 0;
796  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->setItemAvailable(true);
797  }
798  }
799  }
800 
801  PoliceShoot(dt);
802 
803  for (int i = 0; i < Police.ReturnListSize(); ++i)
804  {
805  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan")
806  {
807  police1.PoliceDrive(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),
808  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemRotation(),
809  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ(),
810  80,80,270);
811  }
812  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan2")
813  {
814  police2.PoliceDrive(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),

1062 void SP2::Animate(double dt)
1063 {
1064  if(walk == false)
1065  {
1066  angle += (float)(WSPEED * dt);
1067  translate += (float)(dt);
1068  if(translate < 0)
1069  {
1070  translateY = translate * -1;
1071  }
1072  else
1073  {
1074  translateY = translate;
1075  }
1076  if(angle >= 30)
1077  {
1078  walk = true;
1079  }
1080  }
1081  else if(walk == true)
1082  {
1083  angle -= (float)(WSPEED * dt);
1084  translate -= (float)(dt);
1085  if(translate < 0)
1086  {
1087  translateY = translate * - 1;
1088  }
1089  else
1090  {
1091  translateY = translate;
1092  }
1093  if(angle <= -30)
1094  {
1095  walk = false;
1096  }
1097  }
1098 }

4139 void SP2::RenderMesh(Mesh *mesh, bool enableLight)
4140 {
4141  Mtx44 MVP, modelView, modelView_inverse_transpose;
4142 
4143  MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
4144  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
4145  if(enableLight)
4146  {
4147  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 1);
4148  modelView = viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
4149  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView.a[0]);
4150  modelView_inverse_transpose = modelView.GetInverse().GetTranspose();
4151  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW_INVERSE_TRANSPOSE], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView_inverse_transpose.a[0]);
4152 
4153  //load material
4154  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_AMBIENT], 1, &mesh->material.kAmbient.r);
4155  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_DIFFUSE], 1, &mesh->material.kDiffuse.r);
4156  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SPECULAR], 1, &mesh->material.kSpecular.r);
4157  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SHININESS], mesh->material.kShininess);
4158  }
4159  else
4160  {
4161  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
4162  }
4163 
4164  //mesh->Render();
4165 
4166  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
4167  {
4168  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
4169  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
4170  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
4171  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
4172  }
4173  else
4174  {
4175  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 0);
4176  }
4177  mesh->Render(); //this line should only be called once
4178  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
4179  {
4180  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
4181  }
4182 }

4184 void SP2::RenderText(Mesh* mesh, std::string text, Color color)
4185 {
4186  if(!mesh || mesh->textureID <= 0) //Proper error check
4187  return;
4188 
4189  glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
4190  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 1);
4191  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_TEXT_COLOR], 1, &color.r);
4192  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
4193  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
4194  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
4195  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
4196  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
4197  for(unsigned i = 0; i < text.length(); ++i)
4198  {
4199  Mtx44 characterSpacing;
4200  characterSpacing.SetToTranslation(i * 1.0f, 0, 0); //1.0f is the spacing of each character, you may change this value
4201  Mtx44 MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top() * characterSpacing;
4202  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
4203 
4204  mesh->Render((unsigned)text[i] * 6, 6);
4205  }
4206  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
4207  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 0);
4208  glEnable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
4209 }

4236  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
4237  for(unsigned i = 0; i < text.length(); ++i)
4238  {
4239  Mtx44 characterSpacing;
4240  characterSpacing.SetToTranslation(i * 1.0f+1.5f, 1.0f, 0); //1.0f is the spacing of each character, you may change this value
4241  Mtx44 MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top() * characterSpacing;
4242  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
4243 
4244  mesh->Render((unsigned)text[i] * 6, 6);
4245  }

4247  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 0);

4255 void SP2::RenderUI(Mesh* mesh, Color color, float sizeX,float sizeY,float sizeZ, float x, float y)
4256 {

4258  return;
4259 
4260 
4261  glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
4262 
4263  Mtx44 ortho;
4264  ortho.SetToOrtho(0, 80, 0, 60, -10, 10); //size of screen UI
4265  projectionStack.PushMatrix();
4266  projectionStack.LoadMatrix(ortho);
4267  viewStack.PushMatrix();
4268  viewStack.LoadIdentity(); //No need camera for ortho mode
4269  modelStack.PushMatrix();
4270  modelStack.LoadIdentity(); //Reset modelStack

4273

4275  projectionStack.PopMatrix();

4277  modelStack.PopMatrix();

4280 }
